features: (Seller's Reminder) Per Amazon's policy, try-on of underwear items must be carried out without contact with the body(and with your clothes on) to qualify for return or reimbursement, which is recommended upon the receipt of this pack of underwear for timely determination of the appropriateness of size.

(Built Where it Counts) Composition is the foundation of a good piece of underwear. For these hipster panties, that foundation starts with nylon and Spandex for the whole body to ensure there's enough elasticity to comply to your female undulations and sufficient resistance to shrinkage and ripping. On top of that, the crotch is padded with pure cotton fabric to obliterate chafing and minimize the risk of gynecological ailments.

(Go Commando, with Panties on) Wanna go commando but afraid a puff of wind would reveal your secret as it lifts your skirt? With these hipster panties, that fear ceases to exist. Coming with a mesh structure that's highly breathable, lightweight and extremely good at wicking away moisture, wearing them just feels like wearing nothing. Plus, the time-perfected craftsmanship of our designers makes sure there's no riding up or falling down or digging into your sacred ravines in the front and back.

(Seamless Versatility) Sick and tired of that brazen pantie line hinting at your secret, turning people's heads, and rendering an entire carefully selected outfit invisible? With these panties, that embarrassment just disappears. Crafted with latest sewing techniques, we have successfully made these panties seamless and the most non-picky underwear that goes with any of your outfits.

(You Are What You Wear) Power comes from within. A piece of high-quality, comfy and breathable underwear that speaks to your personality will give you extra power in your daily life as a power woman. Whether you are part of the business elite whose heart is set on sheer black or a housewife who prefers an assortment of basic shades, or a party girl whose verve cannot be represented except by the leopard skin...,we have that exact color for you.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Founded on the belief that comfortable and stylish underwear should be a right and not a privilege, Voenxe was created with a mission to empower people with high-quality, affordable underwear made for every body type. We know that feeling good in your own skin is not just about what you wear on the outside, but what you wear underneath too. That's why we're committed to creating underwear that not only promotes your body positivity but also improves your general well-being. What's in the Package: Seamless Hipster Underwear * 5 Seller's Reminder Gentle hand wash is advised when it comes to the cleaning of these hipsters as washing machines tend to be crawling with germs and tumble dry is extremely harmful to the elasticity and robustness of these hipsters.

Stay Hip Each Day With five colors and patterns packed into one combo, a single pack of these hipster panties allows your lady part to sport a different color each day and to never stay dull and monochrome. Whether you are a stay-at-home good wife or a business woman who's often on the run, these hipsters will keep you comfy and stylish at the same time. All-terrain, All-purpose Hitting the gym for a training session and don't want the sweat you break to keep you from getting that breakthrough? Going to the beach but still want enough coverage for your buttocks? Wanna sport an ultra-thin dress but afraid your underwear becomes the focus? All is realizable with our breathable, perfectly-cut and seamless hipster panties. Fit as if Custom-Made Years of research and development have given us keen insights into the general picture of the size women actually need for their underwear. Ever felt strangled down there because the labeled size was just way off? Been seized in the fear of your panties falling down 'cause the waistband just didn't have enough grip? With these hipster panties, your nether parts can also enjoy custom service.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Comfortable, light weight, and well made. Underwear line under yoga pants isn’t that noticeable. Glad I purchased them. I wear a medium in underwear and I purchased a medium, the fit true to size.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These are hands down the most comfortable underwear EVER! It’s the kind of comfortable that makes you forget you’re even wearing underwear- no digging or pinching or sliding around! The breathable lightweight fabric keeps sweat to a minimum for working out and, despite not being a thong, you can barely see any kind of panty line- you have to really look to see it! Plus I appreciate that they offer the size xs; I’m 5’2” around 103lbs and a size 00-0 so it makes finding underwear that fits well pretty hard. But these fit great! They are not snug and could probably even be a little tighter and still be fine so I’d say they might run a little large but definitely not by much! I feel like every woman needs these! They offer 3 different cuts of underwear and I bought all three kinds and love them all and plan to get some different colors. Because I kind of want to throw away all other underwear and only wear these. Because they are AMAZING! I love hiking, walking, and just being active and these are perfect for that but are just as comfortable for lazy PJ days too! All around AMAZING!BOTTOM LINE (pun intended): HIGHLY recommend. Don’t hesitate, just click buy now!
